column4: Description
str
Affects physical melee damage, as well as damage prevented by parrying and blocking.
Affects physical ranged damage, as well as parry and block rates.
Affects maximum HP.
Affects attack magic potency.
Affects healing magic potency.
Affects maximum MP.
Affects the rate at which you parry attacks with your weapon. The higher the value, the higher the frequency with which you will parry an attack.
Affects amount of damage dealt by physical attacks.
Affects the amount of damage taken by physical attacks. The higher the value, the less damage taken.
Affects the accuracy of both physical and magic attacks. The higher the rating, the better chance your attack will have of landing.
Affects the amount of damage taken by magic attacks. The higher the value, the less damage taken.
Affects the rate at which your physical and magic attacks deal critical damage or restore critical HP. The higher the value, the higher the frequency with which your hits will be critical.
Decreases damage done by slashing attacks.
Decreases damage done by piercing attacks.
Decreases damage done by blunt attacks.
Affects the amount of damage dealt by magic attacks.
Affects the amount of HP restored by healing spells.
Decreases fire-aspected damage.
Decreases ice-aspected damage.
Decreases wind-aspected damage.
Decreases earth-aspected damage.
Decreases lightning-aspected damage.
Decreases water-aspected damage.
Affects the amount of damage dealt by both physical and magic attacks, as well as the amount of HP restored by healing spells. Auto-attack potency is also affected.
Affects the recast timer for weaponskills. The higher the value, the shorter the recast time.
Affects both the casting and recast timers for spells. The higher the value, the shorter the timers.
In PvP, replaces physical and magical defense in determining damage inflicted by other players. Also influences the amount of damage dealt to other players.
Shortens the duration of slow.
Shortens the duration of silence.
Shortens the duration of blind.
Shortens the duration of poison.
Shortens the duration of stun.
Shortens the duration of sleep.
Shortens the duration of bind.
Shortens the duration of heavy.
Affects the amount of progress achieved in a single synthesis step.
Affects the amount of quality improved in a single synthesis step.
Affects the rate at which items are gathered.
Affects the rate at which high-quality items are gathered.
